 Abweichungen davon zu erklären und nach Wegen zu einer Annäherung an den optimalen Pfad unter sich stets verändernden Gegebenheiten zu suchen.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 4aAgrarpolitik. 7aBUSINESS & ECONOMICS / Economics / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Business and Economics 1990 - 1999z9783110635669oZDB-23-GBE0 cprintz978348625246040uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978348680192740uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783486801927423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783486801927/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LAEC  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-GBEc1990d1999